The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Concept is good: Kumar
                                                   Concept is good: Kumar
                      
	Colombo: Newly appointed Sri Lanka captain Kumar Sangakkara Saturday gave a thumbs up to John Buchanans concept of multiple captains.         
	Sangakkara said he understands Buchanans concept because he believes that leadership is always situational.         
	I believe that leadership is always situational. Its a very interesting concept, and I think its all about using the best man for a specific situation. (PTI)                                                                                                                       
